org.keycloak.services.clientpolicy

Interface ClientUpdateContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ClientPolicyContext
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdminClientRegisterContext, AdminClientUpdateContext, DynamicClientRegisterContext, DynamicClientUpdateContext

    public interface ClientUpdateContext
extends ClientPolicyContext
    Represents the context in the client registration/update by Dynamic Client Registration or Admin REST API.
